snippet.title: NASCAR Heat 2 Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
NASCAR Heat 2 arrives September 12 for $49.99. Pre-order now at www.nascarheat.com

Retail editions will include a $50 ticket-coupon redeemable at SMI NASCAR events in 2017 and 2018 (Certain restrictions apply. See insert for details.)

ESRB Rating E for Everyone.
